Bad Lieutenant: Port of Call New Orleans;;57;;86;;R;;Terence McDonagh (Nicolas Cage) isn't doing so well. He has a nasty painkiller addiction, courtesy of an injury he sustained while rescuing a prisoner during Hurricane Katrina. Plus, there's his alcoholic father (Tom Bower), boozy wife (Jennifer Coolidge) and prostitute girlfriend (Eva Mendes). And, he's just been saddled with a rookie partner (Shawn Hatosy). Now Terence must pull himself back from the edge of insanity to investigate a series of murders that has the city on edge.;;Crime,Drama;;Werner Herzog;;2009;;Nicolas Cage,Eva Mendes,Val Kilmer,Xzibit,Fairuza Balk,Shawn Hatosy,Jennifer Coolidge,Tom Bower,Vondie Curtis Hall,Irma P. Hall,Denzel Whitaker,Michael Shannon,Shea Whigham,Lucius Baston;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bad_lieutenant_port_of_call_new_orleans